### Component Categories

#### 1. MODALS

**Standard Modal Structure:**
```jsx
{showModal && (
  <div className="fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div className="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-elevation-lg border-2 border-charcoal-100 w-full max-w-2xl max-h-[90vh] overflow-hidden animate-slide-up">

      {/* Modal Header */}
      <div className="p-6 border-b border-charcoal-100 flex items-center justify-between">
        <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div
            className="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center"
            style={{ background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${theme.gradientFrom}, ${theme.gradientTo})` }}
          >
            <Icon size={20} className="text-white" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 className="font-heading font-bold text-charcoal-900">Modal Title</h3>
            <p className="text-xs text-charcoal-500 font-body">Subtitle or description</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button
          onClick={() => setShowModal(false)}
          className="text-charcoal-400 hover:text-charcoal-700 transition-colors"
        >
          <X size={20} />
        </button>
      </div>

      {/* Modal Body */}
      <div className="p-6 space-y-4 overflow-y-auto max-h-[60vh]">
        {/* Content */}
      </div>

      {/* Modal Footer */}
      <div className="p-6 border-t border-charcoal-100 flex justify-end gap-3">
        <button
          onClick={() => setShowModal(false)}
          className="px-6 py-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-charcoal-600 hover:text-charcoal-900 transition-colors font-body"
        >
          Cancel
        </button>
        <button
          onClick={handleAction}
          disabled={!isValid}
          className="px-6 py-3 bg-charcoal-900 text-white rounded-xl text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-charcoal-800 transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed font-body"
        >
          Action
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
)}
```

**Modal Variations:**
- Success/Celebration: Use `bg-forest-600` for action button
- Danger/Delete: Use `bg-red-600` for action button
- Warning: Use `bg-amber-600` for action button

---

#### 2. GAMIFICATION WIDGETS

**XP Progress Bar:**
```jsx
<div className="bg-white border-2 border-charcoal-100 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-elevation-sm">
  <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
    <span className="text-[10px] font-body text-charcoal-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
      Progress to Next Rank
    </span>
    <span className="text-xs font-body text-charcoal-600 font-bold">
      {current}/{required} XP
    </span>
  </div>
  <div className="h-2 bg-charcoal-100 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
    <div
      className="h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-500"
      style={{
        width: `${percentage}%`,
        background: `linear-gradient(90deg, ${theme.gradientFrom}, ${theme.gradientTo})`
      }}
    />
  </div>
</div>
```

**Streak Display (use StreakFlame component):**
```jsx
import { StreakFlame } from './academy/StreakFlame';

// In render:
{streakDays > 0 ? (
  <StreakFlame streakDays={streakDays} size="sm" /> // or "md", "lg"
) : (
  <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
    <div className="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-charcoal-100 flex items-center justify-center">
      <Zap size={18} className="text-charcoal-400" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <div className="text-[9px] font-body text-charcoal-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">STREAK</div>
      <div className="font-bold text-charcoal-500 text-sm font-heading">Start Today</div>
    </div>
  </div>
)}
```

**Achievement Badge:**
```jsx
<div className="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gold-100 rounded-xl border border-gold-200">
  <Trophy size={16} className="text-gold-600" />
  <span className="text-sm font-bold text-gold-700 font-heading">Achievement Name</span>
</div>
```

**Rank Display:**
```jsx
<div className="flex items-center gap-3">
  <div
    className="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl"
    style={{ background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${theme.gradientFrom}20, ${theme.gradientTo}10)` }}
  >
    {rank.badge} {/* emoji badge from rank system */}
  </div>
  <div>
    <div className="text-[9px] font-body text-charcoal-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">RANK</div>
    <div className="font-bold text-charcoal-900 text-sm font-heading">{rank.title}</div>
  </div>
</div>
```

---

#### 3. STATUS INDICATORS

**Biometric Status (use BiometricStatusIndicator):**
```jsx
import { BiometricStatusIndicator } from './academy/BiometricBackground';

<BiometricStatusIndicator state={state} statusMessage={statusMessage} />
```

**System Status Item:**
```jsx
<div className="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-charcoal-50 border border-charcoal-100 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-elevation-sm transition-all">
  <div className={cn(
    "w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center",
    status === 'success' ? 'bg-forest-100 text-forest-700' :
    status === 'warning' ? 'bg-gold-100 text-gold-700' :
    'bg-charcoal-100 text-charcoal-700'
  )}>
    <Icon size={18} />
  </div>
  <div className="flex-1">
    <div className="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-charcoal-400 font-body">
      {label}
    </div>
    <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
      <span className="font-bold text-charcoal-900 font-heading">{value}</span>
      <span className="text-xs text-charcoal-500 font-body">({detail})</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  {status === 'success' && <CheckCircle size={16} className="text-forest-500" />}
</div>
```

---

#### 4. LIST ITEMS & CARDS

**Notification Item:**
```jsx
<div className={cn(
  "p-6 hover:bg-charcoal-50 transition-colors flex gap-4 items-start group",
  !isRead && "bg-charcoal-50/50"
)}>
  <div className={cn(
    "w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0",
    type === 'success' ? 'bg-forest-100 text-forest-700' :
    type === 'warning' ? 'bg-gold-100 text-gold-700' :
    'bg-blue-100 text-blue-700'
  )}>
    <Icon size={20} />
  </div>
  <div className="flex-1 min-w-0">
    <div className="flex justify-between items-start mb-1 gap-4">
      <h3 className={cn(
        "font-heading font-bold text-sm",
        !isRead ? "text-charcoal-900" : "text-charcoal-600"
      )}>
        {title}
      </h3>
      <span className="text-[10px] text-charcoal-400 whitespace-nowrap font-body">{time}</span>
    </div>
    <p className="text-charcoal-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-body">{message}</p>
    {!isRead && (
      <span className="inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2" style={{ backgroundColor: theme.pulseColor }} />
    )}
  </div>
</div>
```

**Module/Lesson Card:**
```jsx
<div className={cn(
  "bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 overflow-hidden transition-all",
  isActive ? "border-charcoal-900 shadow-elevation-md" : "border-charcoal-100 shadow-elevation-sm hover:shadow-elevation-md"
)}>
  {/* Progress bar at top */}
  <div className="h-1 bg-charcoal-100">
    <div
      className="h-full bg-forest-500 transition-all"
      style={{ width: `${progress}%` }}
    />
  </div>

  <div className="p-6">
    <div className="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div className={cn(
        "w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0",
        isCompleted ? "bg-forest-100" : "bg-charcoal-100"
      )}>
        {isCompleted ? (
          <CheckCircle size={24} className="text-forest-600" />
        ) : (
          <span className="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal-400">{number}</span>
        )}
      </div>
      <div className="flex-1">
        <h3 className="font-heading font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-1">{title}</h3>
        <p className="text-sm text-charcoal-500 font-body">{description}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

---

#### 5. FORM ELEMENTS

**Text Input:**
```jsx
<div>
  <label className="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-charcoal-500 mb-2 block font-body">
    Label
  </label>
  <input
    type="text"
    value={value}
    onChange={(e) => setValue(e.target.value)}
    placeholder="Placeholder text..."
    className="w-full bg-charcoal-50 border-2 border-charcoal-100 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-charcoal-900 transition-all font-body"
  />
</div>
```

**Textarea:**
```jsx
<textarea
  value={value}
  onChange={(e) => setValue(e.target.value)}
  placeholder="Placeholder..."
  className="w-full bg-charcoal-50 border-2 border-charcoal-100 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-charcoal-900 transition-all resize-none h-48 font-mono"
/>
```

**Button Group/Pills:**
```jsx
<div className="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
  {options.map((option) => (
    <button
      key={option.id}
      onClick={() => setSelected(option.id)}
      className={cn(
        "px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold font-body transition-all",
        selected === option.id
          ? "bg-charcoal-900 text-white"
          : "bg-charcoal-100 text-charcoal-600 hover:bg-charcoal-200"
      )}
    >
      {option.label}
    </button>
  ))}
</div>
```

---

### State Management Pattern

```jsx
// Use the academy store hooks
const { xp, rank, streakDays, achievements } = useGamification();
const { score, state, theme, statusMessage } = useBiometric();
const { currentModule, completedLessons } = useAcademyStore();

// Update state
const { addXP, completeLesson, unlockAchievement } = useAcademyStore();
```

---

### STRICT NO-GO LIST

**DO NOT USE:**
- `rounded-full` on buttons/cards (use `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl`)
- Emojis (except rank badges from gamification system)
- Dark mode colors as backgrounds
- Generic placeholder text
- Inline styles for colors that should be dynamic

**DO USE:**
- `font-heading` for titles
- `font-body` for text and labels
- `shadow-elevation-*` for depth
- Biometric colors from `useBiometric()` hook
- `transition-all` or specific transitions
- `cn()` utility for conditional classes

---

### Deliverable

Create component that:
1. Follows the appropriate pattern from above
2. Integrates with academy store if needed
3. Uses biometric-responsive colors where appropriate
4. Has proper accessibility (labels, focus states)
5. Matches the Mission Control aesthetic

